    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Akanthophoreus sp. KK # 3. A, non-ovigerous female (?), habitus; B, pleon lateral view, pleopods omitted for clarity; C – D, antennule, dorsal and lateral view (setae omitted for clarity); E, uropod; F, preparatory male, habitus; G, antennule, lateral view, (setae omitted for clarity). Scale bar = 1 mm for A, B and F, 0.38 mm for E, 0.25 mm for C, D and G." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/178722/files/figure.png" ;
